These are Puzzles for 3x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-1::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: magic-tricks, gardening, sudoku, photography, card-games
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: martial-arts, spy, action, documentary, crime
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: water-polo, lacrosse, snowboarding, sailing, parkour
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who's hobby is photography##1
 2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 4. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
 5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 6. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 7. the person watching spy movies is on the far left##1
 8. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
 9. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
10. the person watching crime movies is the person who's sport is parkour##1
11. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
12. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |      5      |
| Hobby         | gardening    | sudoku  | card-games | magic-tricks    | photography |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | action   | documentary | crime | martial-arts   |
| Sport         | water-polo | lacrosse | sailing  | parkour | snowboarding        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: filmmaking, card-games, photography, board-games, dancing
The people have 5 different jobs:  freelancer, firefighter, mechanic, coach, librarian
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cricket, skiing, basketball, surfing, badminton
 1. the person who's sport is basketball is in an odd position##4
 2. the librarian is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's sport is surfing##2
 3. the librarian is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the firefighter##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in the middle##1
 7. the freelancer is the person who's hobby is photography##1
 8. the firefighter is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
10. the librarian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
11. the coach is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's sport is skiing##2
12. the person who's sport is surfing is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1        |        2        |     3      |         4          |     5     |
| Hobby   | board-games    | card-games         | filmmaking | dancing        | photography   |
| Job     | firefighter | mechanic | coach  | librarian | freelancer |
| Sport   | basketball       | badminton      | surfing   | skiing           | cricket      |

