.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: juice, coffee, mirinda, milk, 7up
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: snowboarding, soccer, ice-hockey, parkour, weightlifting
The people use 5 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, quad-bike, trike, skateboard
 1. the person drinking coffee is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 2. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's sport is soccer##1
 3. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 5. the person drinking juice is between the person driving the motorbike and the person drinking 7up##2
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 8. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is in an even position##4
10. the person drinking mirinda is the person driving the skateboard##1
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person driving the quad-bike##1
12. the person driving the trike is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person driving the skateboard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |    2     |     3      |       4       |     5      |
| Beverage    | mirinda | coffee    | milk   | juice          | 7up      |
| Sport       | ice-hockey    | weightlifting | soccer       | parkour | snowboarding |
| Transport   | skateboard     | trike     | motorbike | bus          | quad-bike     |

