.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, satire, mystery, comedy
5 different pets are kept: frog, fish, lizard, goldfish, rabbit
The people use 5 different means of transport: ship, motorbike, jet-ski, skateboard, trike
 1. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
 3. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
 4. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
 5. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
 7. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 8. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the owner of the rabbit is in an even position##4
10. the person driving the trike is in an odd position##4
11. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left or far right##3
12. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure     | comedy    | satire  | mystery | disaster |
| Pet           | goldfish | fish    | lizard | rabbit  | frog    |
| Transport     | trike      | jet-ski | skateboard    | motorbike    | ship    |

