.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: gospel, funk, salsa, reggae, rock
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, colombian, french, indian, thai
The people use 5 different means of transport: subway, taxi, car, trike, motorbike
 1. the person driving the taxi is the fan of rock##1
 2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
 3. the person driving the car is in an even position##4
 4. the fan of rock is the indian##1
 5. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the subway and the fan of rock##2
 6. the fan of funk is in the middle##1
 7. the argentine is on the left of the colombian##1
 8. the person driving the subway is on the right of the french##1
 9. the thai is on the far right##1
10. the french is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
11. the fan of reggae is the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |    5    |
| Music-Genre   | rock    | gospel        | funk    | salsa      | reggae  |
| Nationality   | indian | french    | argentine | colombian | thai |
| Transport     | taxi   | trike | subway | car      | motorbike   |

