The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: horror, superhero, crime, mystery, animation
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, handball, ice-hockey, volleyball, sailing
 1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 2. the person watching horror movies is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
 5. the person watching crime movies is in an odd position##4
 6. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 7. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
 8. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching horror movies is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
10. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |      3       |    4     |    5     |
| Hobby         | dancing   | magic-tricks  | card-games      | camping  | video-games   |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | horror   | animation     | superhero | mystery  |
