The people prefer 5 different music-genres: r&b, rock, reggae, folk, soul
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, bus, scooter, car, helicopter
 1. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
 2. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4
 3. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 4. the fan of reggae is on the far right##1
 5. the fan of soul is the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 7. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the car is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
10. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left or far right##3
11. the fan of rock is the person driving the bus##1
12. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5    |
| Beverage      | tea  | iced-tea | hot-chocolate | almond-milk   | cola  |
| Music-Genre   | rock  | r&b | soul    | folk        | reggae |
| Transport     | bus | scooter    | motorbike     | car | helicopter    |

