 4. the writer is on the left of the designer##1
 5. the fan of folk is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 6. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the analyst##3
 7. the fan of disco is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 8. the fan of disco is on the right of the designer##1
 9. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left or far right##3
10. the fan of gospel is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |       4       |      5       |
| Hobby         | traveling | skydiving | card-games    | fishing | dancing      |
| Job           | writer | designer | firefighter | analyst    | doctor |
| Music-Genre   | folk        | rock      | disco     | gospel          | hip-hop        |

