.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-9::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, water, soy-milk, iced-tea
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: techno, punk, blues, salsa, classical
5 different pets are kept: pony, goldfish, ferret, guinea-pig, hamster
 1. the person drinking coffee is the fan of salsa##1
 2. the fan of blues is the owner of the hamster##1
 3. the owner of the ferret is the person drinking water##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the fan of punk is the person drinking tea##1
 7. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the owner of the pony is the person drinking tea##1
 9. the fan of classical is in an odd position##4
10. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4
11. the owner of the hamster is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |   3   |    4    |       5       |
| Beverage      | water  | coffee | tea  | iced-tea | soy-milk |
| Music-Genre   | classical | salsa       | punk | techno | blues          |
| Pet           | ferret   | goldfish        | pony   | guinea-pig   | hamster        |

