 4. the person watching horror movies is the designer##1
 5. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 7. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
 8. the owner of the rabbit is between the person watching musical movies and the owner of the goat##2
 9. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
10. the paramedic is the person watching disaster movies##1
11. the designer is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
