.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-11::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, sprite, cola, tea, almond-milk
There 5 different types of food: lemon, cucumber, cabbage, artichoke, cauliflower
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: electronic, pop, gospel, techno, reggae
 1. the person eating lemon is the person drinking tea##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating cabbage##1
 3. the person eating cabbage is on the far right##1
 4. the person drinking tea is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 5. the fan of pop is in an even position##4
 6. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
 7. the fan of electronic is the person drinking cola##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking almond-milk and the fan of gospel##2
 9. the person eating artichoke is in an odd position##4
10. the fan of techno is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5   |
| Beverage      | cola    | tea | sprite   | iced-tea  | almond-milk |
| Food          | artichoke    | lemon  | cauliflower | cucumber | cabbage  |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | pop    | gospel      | techno   | reggae |

