 6. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 8. the person eating cranberry is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far right##1
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3     |     4      |      5      |
