.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-14::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  police-officer, writer, teacher, security-guard, entrepreneur
There are 5 different nationalities: american, british, german, argentine, polish
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, car, jet-ski, boat, skateboard
 1. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the writer##1
 2. the entrepreneur is on the left of the writer##1
