 4. the german is on the left or right of the argentine##3
 5. the american is the teacher##1
 6. the writer is the person driving the car##1
 7. the person driving the jet-ski is between the police-officer and the writer##2
 8. the police-officer is the person driving the boat##1
 9. the german is the person driving the jet-ski##1
10. the polish is the person driving the car##1
11. the argentine is in an odd position##4
12. the argentine is the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3     |         4          |     5     |
| Job           | police-officer | entrepreneur | writer    | security-guard | teacher  |
| Nationality   | argentine     | german    | polish  | british              | american |
| Transport     | boat     | jet-ski       | car | airplane         | skateboard    |

